707981f.title: Manhattan: 2nd Avenue - 127th Street (East)
707981f.text:
Second Ave., at East 127th Street, showing a sewer construction project
by the W.P.A. The view is northward and shows overhead the Second Ave.
Elevated Line.
October 8, 1936.
W.P.A. Photo.
Federal Art Project.
